original_font_information.description: basis33 is a fixed-width font for programming and text editing, which contains Latin, Cyrillic and Hebrew glyphs. It's designed by Manchson based on Latin-only Proggy Clean font by Tristan Grimmer.
original_font_information.sampleText: Five big quacking zephyrs jolt my wax bed
